@kellypatrickxox @cie1947 ...We do not deal in unattributed cultural objects. We are proud to say thisask by Mike Dangeli is currently for sale through Alcheringa, as are all the pieces we post.

@kellypatrickxox @cie1947 Thanks for your enquiry. The answer is that we are an accredited art gallery representing indigenous artists. We practice our business in a good way, with full respect for artists. We deal directly with artists or collectors of fine art which is intended to be sold publicly...
